title: JWT Auth Middleware Pipeline

participant Mobile App as App
participant API Gateway as GW
participant Auth Middleware as Auth
participant Rate Limiter as RL
participant User Service as Users
participant Redis as Redis

App->>GW: GET /api/v1/profile (Bearer eyJhb...)
GW->>RL: Check rate limit (client_ip)
RL->>Redis: INCR rate:192.168.1.50
Redis-->>RL: count=47
note right of RL: Under limit (100/min)
RL-->>GW: Allowed
GW->>Auth: Validate token
Auth->>Auth: Decode JWT header
note over Auth: Verify RS256 + exp + iss claims
Auth->>Redis: GET blacklist:jti:abc123
Redis-->>Auth: (nil)
note right of Auth: Token not revoked
Auth-->>GW: Valid (sub=user_42)
GW->>Users: GET /internal/users/42/profile
Users->>Redis: GET user:42:profile
Redis-->>Users: (nil)
note right of Users: Cache miss
Users->>Users: Query database
Users-->>Redis: SETEX user:42:profile 300 {...}
Users-->>GW: { id: 42, name: "Jane" }
GW-->>App: 200 OK { id: 42, name: "Jane" }
